{"word":"G2029 - ἐποπτεύω - epopteúō - ep-opt-yoo'-o - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐποπτεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epopteúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-opt-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவனி"},{"paragraph":"1. to be an overseer"},{"paragraph":"2. to look upon, view attentively; to watch"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3700 - ὀπτάνομαι - optánomai - op-tan'-om-ahee/3700\">G3700</a>; to <i>inspect</i>, that is, <i>watch:</i> - behold.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2029/2029\">G2029</a>, <a href=\"#/G2030/2030\">G2030</a>, <a href=\"#/G3700/3700\">G3700</a>, <a href=\"#/G3701/3701\">G3701</a>, <a href=\"#/G845/845\">G845</a>, <a href=\"#/G991/991\">G991</a>"}]}